author: Swagata Dam
title: The New Song From Phillauri Is A Peppy Punjabi Dance Number
text:
Swagata Dam Feb . 23 . 2017 
Featuring Diljit Dosanjh and Anushka Sharma , Dum Dum from Phillauri is a soulful rendition that has touched many hearts. And now, the new song from the film, ‘ What’s Up ‘ is here. You can see Life Of Pi actor Suraj Sharma ‘s character getting married in this one. Check out the fun number crooned by Mika Singh and Jasleen Royal . 
Add this to your (or your friend’s) Sangeet playlist now! 0
